   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2408 and MH 2423, recto: (1) I, (2) Tadore, daughter of (3) Korsyne, write (4) to Koloje, (5) completely pure, the woman (6) of Jeme.  I owe (7) her one gold tremis (8)--gold coin, 1 tremis--(9) and this I am prepared (10) by the will of God (11) to pay you in Paone, (12) under Paul, son of Papnoute, (13) the lashane, together with eight maje of (14) interest.  I, Tadore, assent to (15) this sherd.  I...son of...(16) witness.  Ko...(17) witness.</ab>
